OL,3,CJob losses as retailer to shut 13
OL,4,CWelsh stores
OL,6,FZelf Hussain, Joint Administrator for
OL,7,FPwC, said "Carpetright has fallen
OL,8,Fvictim to challenges facing many
OL,9,Fretailers, especially those selling
OL,10,Fbig ticket items.
OL,12,F"A mixture of factors, including a big
OL,13,Freduction in consumer spending due to
OL,14,Fcost of living pressures, lower home
OL,15,Fsales and a debilitating cyber attack
OL,16,Fmade it impossible for the business to
OL,17,Fcontinue in its current form.
