OL,3,CJob losses as retailer to shut 13
OL,4,CWelsh stores
OL,6,F"The sale of some stores and the brand
OL,7,Fto Tapi has allowed over 300 jobs to
OL,8,Fbe saved, and gives the Carpetright
OL,9,Fbrand the chance to continue and
OL,10,Fflourish under its new ownership.
OL,12,F"However, it is deeply saddening that
OL,13,Ffor the remainder of the workforce
OL,14,Fthere will be redundancies.
OL,16,F"We are committed to helping those
OL,17,Faffected and will make sure redundancy
OL,18,Fclaims are processed as quickly as
OL,19,Fpossible. In collaboration with Tapi,
OL,20,Fwe will assist in efforts to help
OL,21,Findividuals find new jobs elsewhere.
